---

<section class="section section-border">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="cta-dark rounded-3xl px-8 py-14 text-center sm:px-12 sm:py-16" data-anim>

      <span class="cta-kicker">Επόμενο βήμα</span>

      <h2 class="mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
        Να σας δείξουμε το Tethys<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        με τα δικά σας πραγματικά σενάρια;
      </h2>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-blue-100/80">
        Κάνουμε σύντομη επίδειξη στη ροή σας και δείχνουμε πώς η πλατφόρμα
        μειώνει θόρυβο, λάθη και καθυστερήσεις.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="/el/contact" class="btn-cta-white">
          Κλείστε παρουσίαση
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/el/product" class="btn-cta-ghost">Δείτε το προϊόν</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-dark {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00244d 0%, #00366b 60%, #004d96 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 36, 77, 0.35);
  }

  .cta-kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .cta-kicker::before {
    content: "";
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #7dd3fc;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .btn-cta-white {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    height: 2.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: none;
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #00366b;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-cta-white:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .btn-cta-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 2.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-cta-ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }
</style>
